<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lie2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lie,</orth> subst. falsehood uttered for the purpose of deception: Ven <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.228" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 228</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 72.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 72, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.138.14" default="NO" valid="yes">138, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 52" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.186" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.107" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 6, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.274" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 274</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.274" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 274</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.249" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.161" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 161</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.330" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 330</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.91" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 6, 161</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.7.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 7, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 32</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>a l. seven times removed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 71</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the l. circumstantial and the l. direct,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 71</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 71</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 71</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.71" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 4, 71</bibl> <cit><quote>as cheap as --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 6, 47</bibl></cit>; cf. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.372" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 372</bibl>. <cit><quote>that's a l. in thy throat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 17</bibl></cit> (Fluellen's speech), <cit><quote>to thrust the l. unto him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 6, 110</bibl></cit>. <emph>to give the l.</emph> == to charge with falsehood (cf. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 132</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.53.132" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 53</bibl>): <bibl n="shak. son 150.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 150, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 85</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 138</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.410" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 410</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.4.90" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.746" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 746</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.746" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 746</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.2.144" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 144</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 2, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.2.100" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.107" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 6, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 40</bibl>. <cit><quote>gives the l. in the throat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.601" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 601</bibl></cit>. <emph>to tell a l.</emph> or <cit><quote>--s:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.248" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 248</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.32" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.324" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 324</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.4.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 4, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.4.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 4, 69</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.209" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 209</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.214" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 214</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.2.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 2, 25</bibl>. Playing on the word: <bibl n="shak. tn 3.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 2, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.66" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 40</bibl>.
